            <h2 class="title"><a href="http://k.lenz.name/LB/?p=10860" rel="bookmark">Bitcoin Based Cap and Trade</a></h2>
        <div class="meta">
		<p>              
                Jul 13 2014
               </p>
	</div>
	<div class="entry">
              <p>New video in the Youtube Bitcoin 101 series about a crazy idea to develop a Bitcoin-based global CO2 cap and trade system called Sno Cap.</p>
<p><iframe width="500" height="281" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/fCtf9eumuhU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>
<p>I just saw this <a href="http://www.reddit.com/r/Bitcoin/comments/2ajikc/even_if_you_dont_care_about_climate_help_to/">at the Reddit Bitcoin forum</a>. I have no idea if it might work. But just like Bitcoin itself is creating a global currency based only on the power of mathematics, it might just be possible to create a global cap and trade system based on the Bitcoin global public ledger.</p>
<p>Anyway, as someone with a strong interest both in Bitcoin and global warming issues, this obviously deserves some attention.</p>
