<li id="linkcat-25" class="widget widget_links"><h2 class="widgettitle">07 Energy from the Desert</h2>

	<ul class='xoxo blogroll'>
<li><a href="http://www.ansole.org/">ANSOLE</a></li>
<li><a href="http://asian-power.com/">Asian Power</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.thegatesnotes.com/GlobalPages/Filter?topic=Energy" title="Bill Gates&#8217; personal website&#8217;s energy tag">Bill Gates</a></li>
<li><a href="http://about.bnef.com/">Bloomberg</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.carbonwarroom.com/">Carbon War Room</a></li>
<li><a href="http://cleantechnica.com/">Cleantechnica</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.climatefinanceoptions.org/cfo/index.php">Climate Finance Options</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.withouthotair.com/" title="The numbers on clean energy">David McKay</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.desertec.org/en/news/" title="Energy from the desert">DESERTEC</a></li>
<li><a href="http://dii-eumena.com/" title="DESERTEC Industrial Initiative">Dii</a></li>
